{"tid":1334781,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"酸自由派愛紙吸管 川普競選網站大賣塑膠吸管","createTime":"2019-07-20T08:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T10:52:23.000Z","uid":150609,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e38ccfaefb853208a16d04e3dab6c8a9832022d","tid":1334781,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:46:30.000Z","msg":"川普競選團隊推出了10支一包的塑膠吸管，售價為15美元（約台幣465元），線上商店還在該商品旁標記「自由派紙吸管沒用」、「支持川普總統，今天就購買可回收吸管」，該吸管外表為川普主打的紅色，並在吸管上有著川普的名字，並標註是可重複使用、可回收、不含BPA、美國製造。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，上週五川普被問到是否支持禁止塑膠吸管，川普回應「塑膠吸管是個有趣的問題，你有一根小小的吸管，<span style=\"color: red;\">但那些盤子、包裝材料以及那些更大的東西呢，它們的原料都是一樣</span>」、「大家都把注意力放在吸管上，還有很多其他的事情需要關注」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oy78bRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foy78bRh.jpg&h=ca368a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQVxDv7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQVxDv7.jpg&h=caa38b3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌打左膠 環保撚臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021166408c3032cf2b428d64ba8b107043e55d57","tid":1334781,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:53:25.000Z","msg":"可重用加可回收塑膠吸管 有錢又有支持率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇到我都想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ef0e71ad025858c3272c0597502f30d59d9ead","tid":1334781,"uid":101481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"海龜出動"},{"pid":"252e27cc2e11adbbcf86dd58851e23059a5bce95","tid":1334781,"uid":33653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21ef0e71ad025858c3272c0597502f30d59d9ead","tid":1334781,"uid":101481,"like":0,"dis